1. Sales Trend Insight
“Sales showed a steady increase from January to November, with a noticeable peak in November — likely due to seasonal promotions or holiday sales. However, December sales dipped, indicating potential fulfillment delays or stockouts.”

🌍 2. Top-Performing Region
“The West region generated the highest overall sales, accounting for approximately 35% of total revenue. It also had a strong profit margin compared to other regions.”

📦 3. Category Performance
“The Technology category leads in both sales and profit, while the Office Supplies category, despite decent sales, has a much lower profit margin — indicating higher cost or lower pricing strategy.”

